{"tid":467370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失聯飛官遭疑投共 馮世寬哽咽爆粗口","createTime":"2017-11-13T12:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T13:29:27.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d915cc1f9e708a465381f35169d3c66174ac8ce3","tid":467370,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:31:08.000Z","msg":"幻象2000戰機，7號晚間演訓過程意外墜機，海空總動員，搜救失聯飛官何子雨。昨天(8號)搜救首度出現明確線索，在雷達光點消失的海域，找到斷斷續續的求救訊號，可惜搜尋至今，還是沒有找到失聯飛官的身影。不過昨天(8號)空軍的記者會上，有媒體質疑，何子雨是不是投共了。結果當時副司令張哲平，回答不太可能，引發批評。國防部長馮世寬今天(9號)在立法院震怒，氣到爆粗口，就是心疼何子雨的忠誠，受到質疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZ4KCqGT_u0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLZ4KCqGT_u0&d=Wqqs1%2FQuREATe5Sljs4VVwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=04ac94b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZ4KCqGT_u0</a>"},{"pid":"9b3ca9457be09ae51ba822595478c392bdb92230","tid":467370,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"台灣傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec59b118e7e27058bff2ccfae79ae13644e53002","tid":467370,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:37:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">狂賀coffee@,極右派政治家被bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"5b0a7d0f362274f57d7f02efa5141621e8d7f011","tid":467370,"uid":68203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問個個都on9,而家咩年代仲要揸架機先可以投共？"},{"pid":"13a47551fc87efb5c0369b859786a9e4b38d79e2","tid":467370,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:46:11.000Z","msg":"國防部進一步表示，在立法院有委員對昨日空軍司令部召開記者說明會，有媒體質疑「何上尉有無投共的可能」時，馮部長身軀高大，平時不怒而威，卻言行平和。然聞此不當提問，馮部長態度堅決，立即義憤填膺地認為，這種說法對於軍人是極大的侮辱，絕對不能接受。以當時何上尉執行夜航訓練時，正是一般民眾下班後與家人團聚共進晚餐的時刻，卻在遠距北部約100浬外執行夜間訓練，為的就是捍衛國家安全，讓廣大的民眾能夠安居樂業。值此國軍及各單位協助投入全力搜救何上尉時刻，媒體不當的提問，讓兢兢業業的軍人及廣大的眷屬同感不平與憤怒。"},{"pid":"2a8922940f4e739a65642bd6e47ce9919a71636e","tid":467370,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">狂賀coffee@,極右派政治家被bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n洗板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae659e38085b1d0a563228b8432cbe9f871a6ea","tid":467370,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台灣傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問個個都on9,而家咩年代仲要揸架機先可以投共？</blockquote><br />\n以強國立場, 依家國軍駕機來投誠冇乜用架, 留在國軍中做無間道仲有價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee79bf2d1f5bce57a327931de5898f22a00fc141","tid":467370,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f442cd47eb962fd56ae9caf8692ed1106600fb","tid":467370,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}